{"tid":1859034,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"首爾市政府：從武漢入境支那人 65名下落不明","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T05:33:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f80fa00bb6af987547b8f24989fea6c1951e7be5","tid":1859034,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"首爾市政府今天表示，1月13日至25日從新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV，武漢肺炎）疫情發源地中國武漢訪問首爾的205名外國人士中，有65人下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n南韓聯合新聞通訊社指出，首爾市與外交部、法務部、出入境管理事務所合作下確認這65人是否出境，並指示首爾地方警察廳追蹤調查。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，1月31日，首爾市獲得韓國疾病管理本部提供的205人（中國籍有185人）名單，與首爾市各區政府共享，並派公務員趕赴他們入境時申報的居所。根據調查，其中的39人已出境，101人接受觀察，65人下落不明。"},{"pid":"0aa1591df5aaa09e37d8a3b9bbf5eeeb22aa01dc","tid":1859034,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"光復漢城，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd391e8ff811e60b9b62142ded9987fa64cfdbb","tid":1859034,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"流亡韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7407bf993f07264f1b9ec747b41c3952880b66","tid":1859034,"uid":180772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人"},{"pid":"28b655557ca95f46a35f38fa7b50021e939e5495","tid":1859034,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡（型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857672</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"327037b7a60501135cd16eaf5f1546ed31615